<br>
Nothing happened.<br>
<br>
Sapphira glared down at her son.<br>
<br>
&quot;You worthless piece of. . &quot; She mumbled as she took out a dagger and struck the boy in the back. He gasped in pain as the blood dripped down his back. He collapsed to the floor and the blood dripped into the portal.<br>
<br>
A large flame came out from the gate and opened the portal completely.<br>
<br>
Sapphira grinned and smiled to her son. &quot;Come now boy.&quot;<br>
<br>
He was alive, but in deep pain.. . <br>
<br>
