<br>
Alysia stood before them all. . . <br>
<br>
&quot;My sisters, we have been called to war. By ourselves.&quot;<br>
<br>
A few of them  mumbled not knowing what to say.<br>
<br>
&quot;You know the stories of Xena and Hercules in another world. An Alternate Universe. Well our &quot;other&quot; selves are all Romans. And they want to come here and fight us. The portal is opened and the war has already begun. I tell you this now, no one fight anyone but your &quot;other&quot; self. If you harm another Roman, one of your sisters will be harmed. If you kill one, you or one of your sisters will die. Remember this, only Wulf can stop the bloodshed, please becareful. Now go and fight for your lives!&quot;<br>
<br>
The amazons immediatly looked to the hill overlooking the village and sure enough a blazing portal was opened and Romans by the numbers were marching out of it. Not just Romans, women. . .women with the skills of amazons.<br>
